{"tid":122063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★港青為符合申請公屋 加薪唔敢要  !","createTime":"2017-02-15T17:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T13:57:27.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"761692c946935aa682340a9de4db1cdb30a94903","tid":122063,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:29:36.000Z","msg":"【晴報專訊】香港地「一屋難求」。有網民自言人工剛好可申請公屋，近日公司有意加薪，他猶豫應否接受，不少網民則揚言寧要公屋不要加薪。有住屋關注團體指，公屋輪候制度僵化，部分人為申請公屋而刻意不工作，變相是約束生產力。<br />\n網上潮文曾說公屋富戶是人生大贏家，又指不少戶主生活好過所謂中產。有網民在討論區留言，聲稱現時收入剛好未過申請公屋的入息上限，最近公司表示會加薪，但加薪後他便不符合申請，事主不禁提問︰「你會要公屋還是加人工」？<br />\n不少網民留言說，寧願要公屋也不要加人工，直言︰「梗係公屋啦！加幾多都唔夠我cover租金」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/newsDetail/headline?headline=港青為符合申請公屋%20加薪唔敢要\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2FnewsDetail%2Fheadline%3Fheadline%3D%E6%B8%AF%E9%9D%92%E7%82%BA%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B%2520%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA%E5%94%94%E6%95%A2%E8%A6%81&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=d800a212\" target=\"_blank\">http://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/newsDetail/headline?headline=港青為符合申請公屋%20加薪唔敢要</a>"},{"pid":"7792b06e140582cf3d67ae671a06ac20d2e5e693","tid":122063,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:30:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">得公屋，得天下！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba88cfce86358e86e22270e9b97ba85545fa9f2","tid":122063,"uid":35296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a